title: 2019 Story Line Over/Unders | Group Chat
description:
We do a little game of "predict the headlines" ahead of the 2019 NBA season: When will Anthony Davis start to get unhappy in L.A.? When will Ben Simmons’s jump shot get called into question? When will we start to worry that Zion is out of shape? And more.

Hosts: Chris Ryan and Justin Verrier
